Program: Discovery
Title: NASA ends the Pathfinder Mission
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrx0g
Last Broadcast Date: 10 November 1997
After losing the signal of the rover on Mars NASA officially ends the Pathfinder mission. Despite having to accept the end of the mission scientists believe it was successful and has paved the way for future missions. Also in the programme researchers studying identical twins genes and the matchbox-sized nano-laboratory. Presenter: Graham Easton. Show less